properties.stmtText:
SUB-2000-PROCESS .
 
MOVE 0 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
MOVE LOW-VALUES TO FAKER-INFO-OCCS
MOVE SPACES TO W-TABLE-2

SUB-9010-FIRST-NAME .
 
MOVE 'FIRST-NAMES-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
MOVE 'FIRST-NAMES-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-2
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FIRST-NAMES-MALE
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-2 TO ADDRESS OF FIRST-NAMES-FEMALE

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
MOVE W-TABLE-1 TO FAKER-TABLE ( FI-DX )

MOVE W-FAKER-FORMAT TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT
MOVE 1 TO W-SUB-1
PERFORM SUB-2110-RECURSE-FORMATS THRU SUB-2110-EXIT UNTIL W-SUB-1 > LENGTH OF W-RECURSED-FORMAT OR NOT FAKER-RESPONSE-GOOD IN L-PARAMETER

MOVE SPACES TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE 1 TO W-SUB-1 W-SUB-2
PERFORM SUB-2120-PROCESS-FORMATS THRU SUB-2120-EXIT UNTIL W-SUB-1 > LENGTH OF W-RECURSED-FORMAT OR W-SUB-2 > LENGTH OF FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER OR W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1 : ) = SPACES

ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
UNSTRING W-RECURSED-FORMAT DELIMITED W-FORMAT-END INTO W-FORMAT-ENTRY POINTER W-SUB-1
STRING W-FAKER-RESULT DELIMITED '  ' INTO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER POINTER W-SUB-2

SUB-9020-FIRST-NAME-MALE .
 
MOVE 'FIRST-NAMES-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FIRST-NAMES-MALE

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
MOVE W-TABLE-1 TO FAKER-TABLE ( FI-DX )

MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9710-FIND-FORMAT THRU SUB-9710-EXIT VARYING L-F-DX-1 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-F-DX-1 > L-FORMAT-ENTRY-CNT-1

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-2 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9720-FIND-FORMAT THRU SUB-9720-EXIT VARYING L-F-DX-2 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-F-DX-2 > L-FORMAT-ENTRY-CNT-2
MOVE 'Random format not found' TO W-FAKER-FORMAT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-F-DX-2
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 'Random format not found' TO W-FAKER-FORMAT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-F-DX-1
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9310-FIND-PERSON THRU SUB-9310-EXIT VARYING L-P-DX-1 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-P-DX-1 > L-PERSON-ENTRY-CNT-1
IF PERSON-NAME OR PERSON-NAME-MALE OR PERSON-NAME-FEMALE

MOVE 1 TO W-POINT
INSPECT FAKER-PERSON-LAST-NAME TALLYING W-POINT FOR CHARACTERS BEFORE SPACE
STRING '-' W-FAKER-RESULT DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-PERSON-LAST-NAME POINTER W-POINT

STRING W-FAKER-FORMAT DELIMITED '  ' INTO W-RECURSED-FORMAT POINTER W-SUB-1-SAVE
MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT-REST TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1-SAVE : )

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT
MOVE W-TABLE-2 TO FAKER-TABLE ( FI-DX )
MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9320-FIND-PERSON THRU SUB-9320-EXIT VARYING L-P-DX-2 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-P-DX-2 > L-PERSON-ENTRY-CNT-2
MOVE 'Random item not found' TO W-FAKER-RESULT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-P-DX-2
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY ( FI-DX )
MOVE 'Random item not found' TO W-FAKER-RESULT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-P-DX-1
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY ( FI-DX )

SUB-9030-FIRST-NAME-FEMALE .
 
MOVE 'FIRST-NAMES-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FIRST-NAMES-FEMALE

SUB-9040-LAST-NAME .
 
MOVE 'LAST-NAMES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF LAST-NAMES

SUB-9090-PREFIX-MALE .
 
MOVE 'PREFIXES-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF PREFIXES-MALE

SUB-9100-PREFIX-FEMALE .
 
MOVE 'PREFIXES-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF PREFIXES-FEMALE

SUB-9120-SUFFIX-MALE .
 
MOVE 'SUFFIXES-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF SUFFIXES-MALE

SUB-9130-SUFFIX-FEMALE .
 
MOVE 'SUFFIXES-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF SUFFIXES-FEMALE

MOVE SPACES TO W-TABLE-1
SET FAKER-UNKNOWN-FORMAT TO TRUE
STRING 'Unknown FAKPERS format "' W-FORMAT-ENTRY '"' DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-RESPONSE-MSG
GO TO SUB-9000-EXIT

MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT-CHAR ( W-SUB-1 ) TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER ( W-SUB-2 : 1 )
ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1 W-SUB-2

ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
GO TO SUB-2110-EXIT

MOVE W-SUB-1 TO W-SUB-1-SAVE
ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
UNSTRING W-RECURSED-FORMAT DELIMITED W-FORMAT-END INTO W-FORMAT-ENTRY POINTER W-SUB-1

MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1 : ) TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT-REST
MOVE W-SUB-1-SAVE TO W-SUB-1

SUB-9050-NAME .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
MOVE 'FORMATS-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-2
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-MALE
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-2 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-FEMALE

SUB-9060-NAME-MALE .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-MALE

SUB-9070-NAME-FEMALE .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-FEMALE

SUB-9080-PREFIX .
 
MOVE 'PREFIXES-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
MOVE 'PREFIXES-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-2
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF PREFIXES-MALE
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-2 TO ADDRESS OF PREFIXES-FEMALE

SUB-9110-SUFFIX .
 
MOVE 'SUFFIXES-MALE' TO W-TABLE-1
MOVE 'SUFFIXES-FEMALE' TO W-TABLE-2
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF SUFFIXES-MALE
SET ADDRESS OF L-PERSON-TABLE-2 TO ADDRESS OF SUFFIXES-FEMALE

SET FAKER-UNKNOWN-FUNCTION TO TRUE
STRING 'Unknown FAKPERS function "' FAKER-PROVIDER-FUNCTION '"' DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-RESPONSE-MSG
GO TO SUB-2000-EXIT

SET W-NOT-FIRST-CALL TO TRUE
MOVE FUNCTION WHEN-COMPILED TO W-COMPILED-DATE
DISPLAY 'FAKPERS  compiled on ' W-COMPILED-DATE-YYYY '/' W-COMPILED-DATE-MM '/' W-COMPILED-DATE-DD ' at ' W-COMPILED-TIME-HH ':' W-COMPILED-TIME-MM ':' W-COMPILED-TIME-SS
PERFORM VARYING FF-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FF-DX > FORMAT-FEMALE-CNT
PERFORM VARYING FM-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FM-DX > FORMAT-MALE-CNT
PERFORM VARYING FNF-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FNF-DX > FIRST-NAME-FEMALE-CNT
PERFORM VARYING FNM-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FNM-DX > FIRST-NAME-MALE-CNT
PERFORM VARYING LN-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL LN-DX > LAST-NAME-CNT
PERFORM VARYING PF-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL PF-DX > PREFIX-FEMALE-CNT
PERFORM VARYING PM-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL PM-DX > PREFIX-MALE-CNT
PERFORM VARYING SF-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL SF-DX > SUFFIX-FEMALE-CNT

PERFORM VARYING SM-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL SM-DX > SUFFIX-MALE-CNT
ADD SUFFIX-MALE-WEIGHT ( SM-DX ) TO SUFFIX-MALE-WEIGHT-TOT
